Plot: Liz Lemon, head writer of the sketch comedy show "TGS with Tracy Jordan", must deal with an arrogant new boss and a crazy new star, all while trying to run a successful TV show without losing her mind.
Title: 30 Rock
Actors: Tina Fey, Tracy Morgan, Jack McBrayer, Scott Adsit
Awards: Won 6 Golden Globes. Another 80 wins & 310 nominations.
